@APIPricingGateway_HostAddress = http://localhost:5064

### Demo 1: Round-Robin Load Balancing
### Hit this repeatedly — Source alternates between Pessimistic and Optimistic.
### Check response headers for X-Served-By and X-Gateway.
GET {{APIPricingGateway_HostAddress}}/getprice
Accept: application/json

###

### Demo 2: Path-Based API Versioning — always routes to Pessimistic Pricing API
GET {{APIPricingGateway_HostAddress}}/v1/getprice
Accept: application/json

###

### Demo 2: Path-Based API Versioning — always routes to Optimistic Pricing API
GET {{APIPricingGateway_HostAddress}}/v2/getprice
Accept: application/json

###

### Demo 3: Random Load Balancing — randomly picks Pessimistic or Optimistic /home
GET {{APIPricingGateway_HostAddress}}/random
Accept: application/json

###

### Demo 4: Rate Limiting — send this 6+ times quickly to trigger a 429 response
GET {{APIPricingGateway_HostAddress}}/getprice
Accept: application/json

###

### Demo 5: Catch-All Route — anything unmatched falls through to Pessimistic /home
GET {{APIPricingGateway_HostAddress}}/this-route-does-not-exist
Accept: application/json

###
